  Description: 'You attack with a weapon you''re wielding or with an unarmed attack,
    targeting one creature within your reach (for a melee attack) or within range
    (for a ranged attack). Roll an attack roll using the attack modifier for the
    weapon or unarmed attack you''re using, and compare the result to the target
    creature''s AC to determine the effect.


    Critical Success You make a damage
    roll according to the weapon or unarmed attack and deal double damage (see Doubling
    and Halving Damage for rules on doubling damage).

    Success You make a damage
    roll according to the weapon or unarmed attack and deal damage.'
